quran[7{c,v,t}:
12,31,"is ne jo unn ki yeh makkarana baatein sunen to unn ko bulawa bhaij diya aur un ke liye takiya daar majlis aaraasta ki aur ziyafat mein har aik ke agay aik churee rakh di ( phir ain is waqt jabkay woh phal kaat kaat kar kha rahi theen ) is ne yousuf ko ishara kya ke un ke samnay nikal aa jab un aurton ki nigah is par pari to woh dang reh gayeen aur apne haath kaat bathain aur be sakhta pakka ray utheen"" HaaSha-Allahہ, yeh shakhs ensaan nahi hai, yeh to koi buzurag farishta hai """
12,32,"Aziz ki biwi ne kaha"" dekh liya! yeh hai yeh woh shakhs jis ke maamla mein tum mujh par baatein banati theen be shak mein ne isay rijhaane ki koshish ki thi magar yeh bach nikla agar yeh mera kehna nah manay ga to qaid kya jaye ga aur bohat zaleel o khawar hoga"
12,33,"yousuf ne kaha"" ae mere rab, qaid mujhe Manzoor hai bah nisbat is ke ke mein woh kaam karoon jo yeh log mujh se chahtay hain aur agar to ne un ki chalon ko mujh se dafaa nah kya to mein un ke daam mein phas jaoon ga aur jahilon mein shaamil ho rahon ga"
12,34,"is ke rab ne is ki dua qubool ki aur unn aurton ki chaalein is se dafaa kar den, be shak wohi hai jo sab ki santa aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
12,35,phir un logon ko yeh sojhi ke aik muddat ke liye usay qaid kar den halaank woh ( is ki pakdamni aur khud apni aurton ke buray atwaar ki ) Sarih nishanain dekh chuke thay
12,36,"qaid khanah mein do ghulam aur bhi is ke sath daakhil hue aik roz unn mein se aik ne uss se kaha"" mein ne khawab mein dekha hai ke mein sharaab kasheed kar raha hon"" dosray ne kaha"" mein ne dekha ke mere sir par rotian rakhi hain aur parinday un ko kha rahay hain"" dono ne kaha"" hamein is ki tabeer bataiye, hum dekhte hain ke aap aik naik aadmi hain """
12,37,"yousuf ne kaha :"" yahan jo khana tumhe mila karta hai is ke anay se pehlay mein tumhe inn khowaboon ki tabeer bta dun ga yeh ilm unn aloom mein se hai jo mere rab ne mujhe ataa kiye hain waqea yeh hai ke mein ne unn logon ka tareeqa chore kar jo Allah par imaan nahi laatay aur akhirat ka inkaar karte hain"
